globalSpecs.name: JASO FC - Meets smoke emission standard

marketing: Shell Advance VSX 2 is a synthetic based lubricant with fragrance, specifically designed for excellent engine protection and performance in 2-stroke motorcycle engines. It guarantees superior control against exhaust system blocking and minimises exhaust smoke. Shell Advance VSX 2 is suitable both for all oil-injection and premix systems and exceeds the requirements of leading manufacturers.
